    narr:generatedFrom "989ab699c1e215e9908c24d1daec9bc0e11a420a" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs the core lexicon and rhetorical architecture defining the [collective memory](narr:Narrative_SIC_KeyPhrases_1) pitch. The discourse is anchored by a set of high-stakes problem framings, most notably the [strategy-execution disconnect](narr:KeyPhrase_StrategyExecutionGap) and the existential risk of [telling state secrets to AI](narr:Observation_StateSecrets). Positioning relies on technical metaphors—[intellectual property as code](narr:Observation_IPAsCode), [steering vector](narr:StyleObs_Metaphor_Vector), and [narrative architecture](narr:StyleObs_KeyPhrase_NarrArch)—to bridge the gap between abstract organizational knowledge and git-native versioning. The narrative trajectory emphasizes a shift from [single-player autosummarization](narr:Observation_MultiplayerShift) toward [intentional memory](narr:Observation_IntentionalMemory), framing the product as a [deepest lever](narr:Observation_DeepestLever) for organizational alignment. Technical grounding is provided by specific definitions for [Memory](narr:Obs_MemoryDefinition) and [Transaction](narr:Obs_TransactionDefinition), while the register oscillates between high-level strategic vision and the [direct, conversational utility](narr:StyleObs_CustomerArchitectPitch_DirectSpeech) of bypassing documentation bottlenecks.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#KeyPhrase_AIContextRich> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#KeyPhrase_StrategyExecutionGap> ;
